== D2L Icons ==

	== Icon ==
		@forEach [&icons] as icon
			${icon}.svg:
				width 100% of ${icon}/width
				height 100% of ${icon}/height
			    aligned horizontally all ${icon}
			    aligned vertically all ${icon}

		&default:
			color-scheme 100% white-#72777a

		&colored:
			color-scheme 100% white-#1c5295

		&sized:
			width 50px
			height 50px

	== Icon Button ==
		@forEach [&buttons] as iconButton
			${iconButton}.icon:
				width 100% of ${iconButton}/width
				height 100% of ${iconButton}/height
				aligned horizontally all ${iconButton}
				aligned vertically all ${iconButton}
